          (act): SiLU(inplace=True)
        )
        (conv3): BaseConv(
          (conv): Conv2d(1280, 1280, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1), bias=False)
          (bn): BatchNorm2d(1280, eps=0.001, momentum=0.03, affine=True, track_running_stats=True)
          (act): SiLU(inplace=True)
        )
        (m): Sequential(
          (0): Bottleneck(
